{"tid":411461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子雍景臺墮樓　飛越窄巷倒高雲臺泳池邊亡","createTime":"2017-09-23T20:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T02:58:11.000Z","uid":122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ba92fd85e06e64cdf77cd26af15958d4fbfb6ae","tid":411461,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:00:15.000Z","msg":"9月23日(六) 22:57更新     21:47建立<br />\n<strong>男子雍景臺墮樓　飛越窄巷倒高雲臺泳池邊亡</strong><br />\n<br />\n西半山發生墮樓案件。一名24歲姓林男子，晚上8時許，在羅便臣道70號雍景臺2座一單位，自行走到大廈天台，其後一躍而下，中年漢跨越衛城坊，再直飛西摩道2號高雲臺私人泳池旁邊，頭顱爆裂。有人見狀，慌忙報警。救護員到場，證實男子當場死亡。警方現場未有檢獲遺書，初步調查事件無可疑。據了解，男死者有情緒病紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線：2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒：18288<br />\n社會福利署：2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)：2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園：18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線：2466 7350<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cc0fdb01906d7a3270ba0ad1efab0595876b8f","tid":411461,"uid":10538,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:04:36.000Z","msg":"24歲 中年漢？"},{"pid":"44615ebd58f7f168943e07c169bbcb811ee39492","tid":411461,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:05:41.000Z","msg":"好似好高難度"},{"pid":"45f71a40f4bbbb7332ec89f2f72ad07cecab161b","tid":411461,"uid":32828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:07:30.000Z","msg":"咁應該係花式跳水定花式跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f0110bcdcf1446b760027d2cef253cd82870b8","tid":411461,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:08:29.000Z","msg":"半山凶宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1221b902a0653d8231ad8415ed4ec1f5114421d","tid":411461,"uid":53121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:08:29.000Z","msg":"以後又多左個靈探新熱點：半山猛鬼泳池"},{"pid":"ec8d5d167704dbc2e1d90a50e76d